_sText:
Disclaimer: This map is extremely spooky, you will be spooked. It is not advised to play this map alone or in the dark. You have been warned.

Now that is out of the way this is a little 40 second or so strafe map I spent the last week or two on.

Oh and the gameplay of this map isn't really similar to winter or summer land at all but I saw the opportunity and I took it.

There is one bonus that you can get to from the teleporter at the end of the map.
